{
  "id": "699bd9616a9c522ab2c39a4b",
  "title": "Current Focus Context",
  "created": 1771821411,
  "updated": 1771821536,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "699bd9616a9c522ab2c39a4b",
      "text": "Current Focus Context",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1771821411,
      "updated": 1771821411
    },
    {
      "id": "699bd9600000000000b27dfe",
      "text": "なんていうか、「今フォーカスしてる対象」という種類の文脈があると思った。",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1771821411,
      "updated": 1771821526
    },
    {
      "id": "699bd9d50000000000b27e0a",
      "text": "捉えておきたいので名前つけてページ化しておくか",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1771821527,
      "updated": 1771821536
    },
    {
      "id": "699bd9880000000000b27e06",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1771821450,
      "updated": 1771821450
    },
    {
      "id": "699bd9610000000000b27e00",
      "text": "例",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1771821411,
      "updated": 1771821412
    },
    {
      "id": "699bd9620000000000b27e02",
      "text": "\t[Obsidian]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1771821412,
      "updated": 1771821415
    },
    {
      "id": "699bd9650000000000b27e03",
      "text": "\t\tCLIが「今開いてるページ」を認識してくれる",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1771821415,
      "updated": 1771821424
    },
    {
      "id": "699bd99b0000000000b27e07",
      "text": "\t\tこのページの契機[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1771821469,
      "updated": 1771821475
    },
    {
      "id": "699bd96e0000000000b27e04",
      "text": "\t[秀丸エディタ]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1771821424,
      "updated": 1771821427
    },
    {
      "id": "699bd9710000000000b27e05",
      "text": "\t\t「最後に編集した行」という概念があって、そこにジャンプしたりできる",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1771821427,
      "updated": 1771821442
    },
    {
      "id": "699bd9620000000000b27e01",
      "text": "\tクリップボード？\t",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1771821412,
      "updated": 1771821499
    },
    {
      "id": "699bd9b90000000000b27e09",
      "text": "\t\t個人的に「クリップボード内容を生成AIに投げる」系のツールをよくつくるが、含められるか？[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1771821499,
      "updated": 1771821515
    },
    {
      "id": "699bd9b40000000000b27e08",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5a4873ab2e26fb001479d3a9",
      "created": 1771821494,
      "updated": 1771821494
    }
  ]
}